<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Digital Presentation</title>
    <style>
        /* Modern Reset and Base */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        /* Centered Container */
        .wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            table-layout: fixed;
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            padding-top: 40px;
            padding-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .main {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 650px;
            border-spacing: 0;
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #2b3a42;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.4); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.02); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.6); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.4); }
        }

        /* Header Area */
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #3498db 100%);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header svg {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            fill: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        /* Body Content area */
        .content {
            padding: 40px 35px;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #4a5568;
        }

        .content a {
            color: #3498db;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        /* Interactive Dynamic Content blocks from LLM */
        .ai-wrapper {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
            padding: 20px 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }

        /* SVG Data Visualizations inline */
        .graph-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 35px 0;
        }

        .graph-label {
            font-size: 13px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: block;
        }

        /* Call To Action Button */
        .btn-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0 20px;
        }

        .btn {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #3498db, #2980b9);
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 35px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.4);
            animation: pulse 3s infinite ease-in-out;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #94a3b8;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .header { padding: 30px 20px; }
            .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
            .main { border-radius: 0; box-shadow: none; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <center class="wrapper">
        <table class="main" width="100%">
            <!-- Header -->
            <tr>
                <td class="header">
                    <!-- Brand / Growth SVG Icon -->
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M16 6l2.29 2.29-4.88 4.88-4-4L2 16.59 3.41 18l6-6 4 4 6.3-6.29L22 12V6z"/>
                    </svg>
                    <h1>Strategy Proposal for {{ business_name }}</h1>
                </td>
            </tr>
            
            <!-- Body Content -->
            <tr>
                <td class="content">
                    <p>Hi there,</p>
                    
                    <div class="ai-wrapper">
                        {{ ai_body_html | safe }}
                    </div>

                    <!-- Inline SVG Chart Representation -->
                    <div class="graph-container">
                        <span class="graph-label">Digital Presence Potential Growth</span>
                        <!-- Using inline styling for cross-client support in email SVGs -->
                        <svg width="300" height="150" viewBox="0 0 300 150">
                            <!-- Axis -->
                            <line x1="30" y1="130" x2="280" y2="130" stroke="#cbd5e1" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <line x1="30" y1="20" x2="30" y2="130" stroke="#cbd5e1" stroke-width="2"/>
                            
                            <!-- Current (Left Bar) -->
                            <rect x="70" y="80" width="50" height="50" fill="#94a3b8" rx="4">
                              <animate attributeName="height" from="0" to="50" dur="1s" fill="freeze" />
                              <animate attributeName="y" from="130" to="80" dur="1s" fill="freeze" />
                            </rect>
                            <text x="95" y="145" font-size="12" fill="#64748b" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Arial, sans-serif">Current</text>
                            
                            <!-- Future (Right Bar) -->
                            <rect x="170" y="30" width="50" height="100" fill="#3498db" rx="4">
                              <animate attributeName="height" from="0" to="100" dur="1.5s" fill="freeze" />
                              <animate attributeName="y" from="130" to="30" dur="1.5s" fill="freeze" />
                            </rect>
                            <text x="195" y="145" font-size="12" fill="#64748b" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Arial, sans-serif">Projected</text>

                            <!-- Growth line connecting tops -->
                            <polyline points="95,75 195,20" fill="none" stroke="#2c3e50" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="5,5">
                                <animate attributeName="stroke-dashoffset" from="150" to="0" dur="2s" fill="freeze" />
                            </polyline>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    
                    <p>We've attached a detailed PDF outlining specific strategies that can help elevate your brand in the local market.</p>

                    <div class="btn-container">
                        <a href="mailto:{{ reply_email }}?subject=Let's discuss strategy for {{ business_name }}" class="btn">Let's Connect</a>
                    </div>
                    
                    <p>Best regards,<br><strong>Your Growth Partner</strong></p>
                </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <tr>
                <td class="footer">
                    <p>Prepared securely and autonomously for <strong>{{ business_name }}</strong></p>
                    <p>Not interested in scaling right now? <a href="mailto:{{ reply_email }}?subject=Unsubscribe">Unsubscribe</a></p>
                    <img src="{{ app_url }}/api/v1/track/open/{{ tracking_token }}" width="1" height="1" style="display:none;" />
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </center>
</body>
</html>
